Review Existing Story (1–2 minutes)

Identify gaps in clarity, structure, or missing information.
Rewrite Title and Description (2–3 minutes)

Update the title for clarity.
Follow the "As a [user role], I want [feature], so that [value]" format for the description.
Define or Refine Acceptance Criteria (3 minutes)

Ensure measurable, testable, and clear criteria.
Update Definition of Ready (2–3 minutes)

Add necessary preconditions.
Update Definition of Done (2–3 minutes)

Clearly define completion criteria, including testing, documentation, and code review.
Final Review (1–2 minutes)

Verify alignment with Scrum principles and team goals.
